{"tid":2088437,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：反政府思維亂港 中央出手理所當然","createTime":"2020-07-01T06:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T06:53:52.000Z","uid":7542,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ee0c27b4ecc217e4b8648017a0cda3d6b6f502a0","tid":2088437,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>終於講到出口，反對政府嘅思想都唔可以有 </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥在有關《港區國安法》的記者會提到，中央希望借今次立法，完善一國兩制體系。她說回歸以來一國兩制實行時有地方未完善，一是未有好好認真嚴肅處理一國與兩制的關係；二是特區未能完善國家安全制度，按基本法23條就7類危害國家安全行為立法；三是未做好推廣國家歷史、民族文化宣傳教育工作；四是未能有效深化促進特區與中央發展關係。<br />\n<br />\n她說這四方面的問題，令香港出現危險風險，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">尤其是有本地激進分子、反政府思維及外部勢力形成張力，令香港社會一觸即發，自去年6月起的暴亂令中央感到要出手。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535173-20200701.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535173-20200701.htm&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbrrngSbsgLaTM31cPJ1174U%3D&h=d3d60a9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535173-20200701.htm&h=07793e12\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535173-20200701.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi7ZF_dgqG3s&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbrrngSbsgLaTM31cPJ1174U%3D&h=4ba80c22\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s</a>"},{"pid":"fe8d5c545979d58259779adc4cc8766001865684","tid":2088437,"uid":10290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:51:05.000Z","msg":"好撚出奇<br />\n一國一制同大陸接軌<br />\n屌一次政府等人拍門喇"},{"pid":"439973d79d03151116324b883eca436d83a1b153","tid":2088437,"uid":39872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T06:51:21.000Z","msg":"世界行緊黑暗法對付